  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 7
  Paragraph: 2
Title: Fit For Emperors And Kings
---
Chien Wu went to see the madman Chieh Yu. Chieh Yu said, "What was
Chung Shih telling you the other day?"  Chien Wu said, "He told me
that the ruler of men should devise his own principles, standards,
ceremonies, and regulations, and then there will be no one who will
fail to obey him and be transformed by them."
